<section class="text">
<p>Being No1 means waiting to see what the opposition comes up with..............so over to you Microsoft.</p></section>
<ul class="ui-comment-tools"><li class="likes first last"><a title="Like this comment" rel="nofollow" class="ui-like" data-subject="comments/5747426" href="login"><span class="icon icon-heart"></span> <span class="value likes">1</span></a></li></ul>
