<section class="text">
<p><a href="https://www.pushsquare.com/users/SirAngry" class="mention" data-username="SirAngry" rel="nofollow">@SirAngry</a> While I see your point I though the $421 was the BOM or bill of materials i.e. the cost of the components ONLY, and also thought to be a low estimate, others thought more. This doesn't include manufacturing, R&amp;D, advertising, distribution, a cut for retailers and other costs. Putting out a console costs far more than the BOM.</p>
<p>As a consumer I hope you're right though and I'm probably setting my expectations low <i title="&#58;wink&#58;"class="twa twa-lg twa-wink"></i></p>
</section>
